           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      55                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-cin-ita        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-cin-ita-999.
