      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo testata : IBAN e BBAN               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cod-ibn-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * IBAN                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EI"                 to   w-cod-cod-cin-ope      .
           move      "IT"                 to   w-cod-cod-cin-naz      .
           move      w-tes-cin-eur        to   w-cod-cod-cin-chd      .
           move      w-tes-cin-ita        to   w-cod-cod-cin-cod      .
           move      w-tes-abi-ban        to   w-cod-cod-cin-abi      .
           move      w-tes-cab-ban        to   w-cod-cod-cin-cab      .
           move      w-tes-sgl-ccb        to   w-cod-cod-cin-ccc      .
           perform   cod-cod-cin-cll-000  thru cod-cod-cin-cll-999    .
       vis-cod-ibn-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione IBAN                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      15                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      18                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-cod-cod-cin-edt    to   v-alf                  .
      *
           if        w-cod-cod-cin-edt    =    spaces
                     move  "(NON DETERMINATO)"
